## Naming conventions

| Artifact | Convention |
|----------|-----------|
| DB key constant | `<Entity>_DbKey` |
| DB type | `DB_<Entity>` |
| Prototype type | `DatabaseDef_<Entity>` |
| UI type | `UI_<Entity>` |
| Database constant | `DBDef_<Entity>` |
| Modifiable validator | `<Entity>_modifiablePropsValidator` |
| Generated validator | `<Entity>_generatedPropsValidator` |
| BE module class | `ModuleBE_<Entity>DB_Class` |
| BE module singleton | `ModuleBE_<Entity>DB` |
| BE module pack | `ModulePackBE_<Entity>` |
| FE module class | `ModuleFE_<Entity>_Class` |
| FE module singleton | `ModuleFE_<Entity>` |
| FE module pack | `ModulePackFE_<LibName>` |
| Dispatcher interface | `On<Entity>Updated` |
| Dispatcher instance | `dispatch_on<Entity>Changed` |
